About Us

Spuceitup is known for its eco-friendly, quality landscaping that our clients on Vancouver Island appreciate and trust. We approach every project with care and meticulous detail, from small neighbourhood gardens to sprawling lawns and commercial spaces. We believe in building lasting relationships with our clients, getting to know them and their styles so that we can best bring their vision to life.

Services

Lawn Care

Our custom Lawn Care services provide solutions for a variety of outdoor spaces. We cater to the needs and requirements of every client, guaranteeing you will get precisely what you want.

Garden Design

Keep your property in tip-top shape with our Garden Design services. Our team does it all and is ready to provide complete attention to your every need. You can count on us to ensure you are satisfied with the results.

Seasonal

We specialize in seasonal services, collaborating with our clients to best express their unique and personal vision for their property. When you work with us, you can expect reliability, timeliness and exceptional work.
